title: Whimsey the Aristocratic Detective and the Ghosts of Highgate
description: Victorian London will never be the same after rambunctiousNew York twins, Panda and Poppy Wilcox, arrive to spend afun-filled summer with their Uncle Whimsey.Unbeknownst to the twins seeing the sights will have to wait,as secrets are revealed, a mystery unfolds, and a new adventure begins.
author: Jolie Nicole Shanoian
